<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Sir Thumper — Celestial Guardian</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

<div id="loader">
  <div class="spinner"></div>
  <p>Summoning Sir Thumper...</p>
</div>

<header class="character-hero">
  <div class="character-image">
    <img src="https://a-z-animals.com/media/2022/05/Keep-rabbits-out-of-your-garden-header.jpg" alt="Sir Thumper">
  </div>

  <div class="character-info">
    <h1>Sir Thumper</h1>
    <p class="character-title">🌌 Divine Meadow Guardian</p>
    <div class="rank-badge">SSS Tier</div>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="lore-section">
  <h2>Legendary Lore</h2>
  <p>
    Forged beneath the aurora skies, Sir Thumper commands the cosmic carrots
    and protects the Meadow from shadowed fox spirits. His paws echo through
    dimensions, bending petals and starlight to his will.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="abilities-section">
  <h2>Celestial Abilities</h2>

  <div class="ability-card">
    <h3>✨ Starfall Hop</h3>
    <p>Leaps into the sky and crashes down in radiant stardust.</p>
    <div class="power-bar"><div style="width: 95%"></div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="ability-card">
    <h3>🌸 Sakura Shield</h3>
    <p>Summons a rotating blossom barrier of pure light.</p>
    <div class="power-bar"><div style="width: 88%"></div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="ability-card">
    <h3>🥕 Cosmic Carrot Beam</h3>
    <p>Fires a concentrated beam of aurora energy.</p>
    <div class="power-bar"><div style="width: 99%"></div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="ability-card">
    <h3>🌙 Moonstep Mirage</h3>
    <p>Creates illusionary copies across the meadow.</p>
    <div class="power-bar"><div style="width: 90%"></div></div>
  </div>

</section>

<nav class="nav-back">
  <a href="index.html">← Return to Homepage</a>
</nav>

<script>
  setTimeout(() => {
    document.getElementById("loader").style.display = "none";
  }, 900);
</script>

</body>
</html>